sg":"你好勇敢，我唔想比人見到我得自己一個買，成日飯都無得食，去拎兩盒牛油拎兩盒糖漿算"},{"pid":"b1e00a9567ca09d216ad7627975aeea6f23ceba1","tid":396841,"uid":30922,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:36:05.000Z","msg":"ching咁蠢既<br />\n我去開殘廁食"},{"pid":"d7243a8cee66d13411f81163679ad1a5f0316254","tid":396841,"uid":25964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"廁所靜靜地 真係唔差"},{"pid":"56dd158fb4c370971b6e2f208aca9cce13a19a44","tid":396841,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10530196bd2f221fa0e3ebcf212bf3cdf0386d3","tid":396841,"uid":56308,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"樓主fm，通常fm先介意呢d野。其實一星期五日要日日都同fd夾到時間一齊食唔容易，自己一個食唔代表自己好毒。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果你係星期一到五都自己食就真係好毒啦"},{"pid":"b04f4f38293ae58e21ba48115f033a1299a7f132","tid":396841,"uid":41821,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"wadiu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係毒到咁呀<br />\n一個食so what?"},{"pid":"35c4c5ef890dc361fc9ddc11cececa5f857ad4bd","tid":396841,"uid":133847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:50:24.000Z","msg":"識食一定係後樓梯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab2c2e2b4367f2a7953c962d08acdf5c926d82b","tid":396841,"uid":125663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"人地唔識你，無人會理你。"},{"pid":"b62199c023acc29965a894829c97b64625cda028","tid":396841,"uid":125663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地唔識你，無人會理你。</blockquote><br />\n你諗多左。就算識你既, 唔通內心恥笑咩？ 有咩好笑？ 唔識你既，更加唔洗驚。"},{"pid":"841be94ddcc2315333e0914d12beb2d7df72f888","tid":396841,"uid":50021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:53:45.000Z","msg":"屎味撈飯"},{"pid":"cab0e0a730862ad02ceb4fbbb361665d9c1efe2e","tid":396841,"uid":72894,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:55:29.000Z","msg":"唔好睇得自己咁重要，以為成日有人留意住你先得架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nYear 1，2，3 幾乎日日自己食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8657f9f3a39a507c7a7fa8864e4a0cee7d18e9dd","tid":396841,"uid":137178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識食一定係後樓梯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去左真係返唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"fd89fe12f96fddbb53ae019d2475a52c6394a194","tid":396841,"uid":34222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:02:47.000Z","msg":"試過上天台食<br />\n<br />\n不過而家天氣熱 好曬<br />\n<br />\n迫住入廁格食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc1982e09bbc67eded75fab6f54342b36e49da3","tid":396841,"uid":7466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:07:58.000Z","msg":"其實你毒撚一個人坐係度食都無人會注意到你架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651432ac88d4ee1f1c219eb5323e827487435e32","tid":396841,"uid":113697,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主fm，通常fm先介意呢d野。其實一星期五日要日日都同fd夾到時間一齊食唔容易，自己一個食唔代表自己好毒。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果你係星期一到五都自己食就真係好毒啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時候，堂與堂之間可能得半小時俾你食，或你得閒時，朋友有堂等等種種情況，一個人食更方便。有時候，太疲累，真係番屋企煮個快餐，食完就訓。所以朋友聚會同食飯都係留番六日好"},{"pid":"445faf2fe9e07a08398b6555b35eb62f83823f17","tid":396841,"uid":2346,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好睇得自己咁重要，以為成日有人留意住你先得架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nYear 1，2，3 幾乎日日自己食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個心態就岩<br />\n就算係朋友都唔一定要一齊食飯<br />\n諗下坐埋一齊但係個個都玩電話<br />\n咁我寧願自己食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c55f8163eebd5927d6edf82601e520973390036","tid":396841,"uid":15370,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:17:23.000Z","msg":"就係你條仆街搞到我冇位痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd82ad251759fd5e1657be255fd69dd2674ac97","tid":396841,"uid":32298,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:29:02.000Z","msg":"有無女人喺廁所傾點殺男人"},{"pid":"d5140eb04721480e3c06e2c42fd154cb309d255c","tid":396841,"uid":136472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:29:30.000Z","msg":"canteen 好多單拖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd6a3a237a894233600998a1341b5e39d12df54","tid":396841,"uid":135689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"識既都撞曬時間 第二個禮拜獨食獨等車"},{"pid":"073059eff61cd855ac79eaaabdac9c2077fcefc4","tid":396841,"uid":136113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"成日自己食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇特登搵人夾timetable<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太煩"},{"pid":"828379acb1bc5a6a1a8a6909050919dde5951d8f","tid":396841,"uid":34767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"樓豬唔好咁自我中心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撚得閒有人理你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係canteen食都唔會有人留意到你既存在架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你咁樣霸撚住個廁所都係想引人注意啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03b55c2176bc75b91770920afc3b9599b6c1277","tid":396841,"uid":136113,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"其實自己食咗一陣就會上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而唔鐘意一班人要一路食一路講野"},{"pid":"a4a1e13dfb1cf5bcb4aa40b1a41e876e448aa3ae","tid":396841,"uid":53515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:38:27.000Z","msg":"我幾乎9成時間都自己食，食乜同咩時間都可以自己決定。<br />\n<br />\n唔通好似中學生咁要一齊去廁所咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62203337720c0a09fb70426cfe72292728a917e2","tid":396841,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:46:32.000Z","msg":"真係毒撚先咁重自尊心<br />\n大學生涯 有邊個未試過一個人食飯<br />\n邊可能日日都夾到人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1dfdb92f1f2990a1ad517326a775e3844a389c","tid":396841,"uid":12680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"隔離條友痾屎點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ba2c595c6410ae1d44278da882b3cf5295e436","tid":396841,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"渣嫁"},{"pid":"0bc0ad807fba12176776cd198318786705cddcbf","tid":396841,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"隔離條友屙爛屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70dfad5060a1338aa14844571172b380f61e254","tid":396841,"uid":89166,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"日日自己食<br />\n最尷尬係見到個識既同科同學<br />\n佢又認得你你又認得佢<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就同其他同科既人食 自己就一個食<br />\n食完大家係下堂既lecture hall 見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe2f4fa0a9ab7ce6755f702c6374b705f337ed4