:"6661d82cc4aa64939d3ada32f879fad3a0cd002b","tid":396841,"uid":25512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"冇人笑你<br />\n係你自己笑自己姐<br />\n利申 成日自己一個食飯"},{"pid":"2f7822a1a95f33a010e6e0a50b1242a9185ca8f7","tid":396841,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗理人點睇認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">就算我有朋友同我一齊食 見到人自己一個食 根本就唔覺得係一件乜野事</span> 而且我亦唔會記住嗰個人(係根本唔會記得)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有人地絕對唔會笑你架 仲小學中學雞咩 讀大學個個都成熟啦 樓主你都要放開你自己個心態同心魔 做人連食飯都要驚人點諗好辛苦 自己食諗下將來點plan仲好啦 定d黎 d朋友慢慢出現架啦 唔洗急<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19659064e873f7e7dcd35a7f9eedf8ea78a2221a","tid":396841,"uid":134636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:48:54.000Z","msg":"我曾經都好介意人地點睇我，但係成個canteen 全部都係一個人坐，真係冇人理你"},{"pid":"46272a0b4ebcdc35dbbe4f2128d86c4675ec83a2","tid":396841,"uid":75046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:55:42.000Z","msg":"其實自己一個食canteen有乜問題<br />\n啲同學時間表都唔會同你一樣架啦"},{"pid":"10eff60cbc9f78b7c7afa05bc8c000b9fdfe5440","tid":396841,"uid":71373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:56:26.000Z","msg":"最尾個句笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f082b0b662d4862fd28ee3e51e58ee43db656a7f","tid":396841,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:02:37.000Z","msg":"on9大把人自己一個食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49432641dc5145156704f19a6c815bc76c21d9b","tid":3968